# Prompt History

SQLite database at `~/.claude/prompt-history.db` tracks:
- **prompts**: Auto-logged via hook, rated at /handoff (utility 1-5, tags)
- **commits**: Git commits linked to sessions
- **sessions**: Session start/end times per project

Hook at `~/.claude/hooks/log-prompt.sh` auto-captures all prompts.
/handoff shows unrated prompts for optional rating.
/readup surfaces high-utility (4+) prompts from past sessions.
/prompts queries history (filters: project, `rated`, `tag:<name>`).

